    "content": "## ⚠️ Superseded — Use the Hub Instead\n\nThis template is no longer the source of truth. Every client's ad account details now live in the Revital Hub's **Client Ad Account Log** (hub.revitalproductions.com → Account Management), a real structured tracker instead of a copy-paste doc. This page stays for historical reference only — new entries go in the Hub.\n\n## Client Ad Account Log Template\n\n## Operations Space — Tools & Tech Stack | Internal Use Only\n\nHOW TO USE: Copy the log entry below every time you onboard a new client with active ad accounts.\n\nCreate one entry per client — logging all their ad platforms in one place. Paste it as a new page in this doc for each client. Never type passwords or payment details directly into ClickUp — store them in the approved password manager only.\n\n## AD ACCOUNT LOG — [CLIENT NAME]p\\\n\n## Copy everything below this line for each new client\n\n## Client Information\n\n- Client Name:\n- Company:\n- Primary Ad Contact:\n- Contact Email:\n- Contact Phone:\n- Billing Contact (if different):\n- Billing Email:\n## Overall Ad Budget\n\n- Total Monthly Ad Spend Budget: $\n\n## Meta (Facebook & Instagram) Ad Account\n\n- Business Manager Name:\n- Business Manager ID:\n- Ad Account Name:\n- Ad Account ID:\n- Access Type: (e.g. Partner Access / Direct Admin)\n- Our Access Level: (e.g. Admin / Advertiser / Analyst)\n- Pixel ID:\n- Pixel Verified & Firing: Yes / No / Not Set Up\n- Billing Method: (e.g. Client's card on file / Our card — specify)\n- Monthly Spend Limit Set: Yes / No — Limit: $\n- Facebook Page Linked: Yes / No — Page Name:\n- Instagram Account Linked: Yes / No — Handle:\n- Account Status: Active / Restricted / Flagged / Disabled\n- Notes:\n## Google Ads Account\n\n- Google Ads Account Name:\n- Customer ID (CID):\n- Manager Account (MCC) Linked: Yes / No — MCC ID:\n- Access Type: (e.g. Manager Account Link / Direct Admin)\n- Our Access Level: (e.g. Admin / Standard / Read Only)\n- Conversion Tracking Set Up: Yes / No\n- Google Tag / GTM Active: Yes / No\nLinked to GA4: Yes / No — GA4 Property ID:\n\n- \n## TikTok Ads Account\n\n- TikTok Business Center Name:\n- Ad Account ID:\n- Access Type: (e.g. Partner Access / Direct Member)\n- Our Access Level: (e.g. Admin / Operator / Analyst)\n- TikTok Pixel Installed: Yes / No / Not Set Up\n- TikTok Account Linked: Yes / No — Handle:\n- Billing Method: (e.g. Client's card / Prepaid balance)\n- Monthly Spend Limit Set: Yes / No — Limit: $\n- Account Status: Active / Restricted / Pending\n- Notes:\n## LinkedIn Ads Account\n\n- LinkedIn Campaign Manager Name:\n- Account ID:\n- Access Type: (e.g. Account Manager / Campaign Manager / Viewer)\n- LinkedIn Page Linked: Yes / No — Page Name:\n- Insight Tag Installed: Yes / No / Not Set Up\n- Billing Method: (e.g. Client's card on file)\n- Monthly Spend Limit Set: Yes / No — Limit: $\n- Account Status: Active / Restricted\n- Notes:\n\n- Access Type:\n- Access Level:\n- Billing Method:\n- Monthly Spend Limit: $\n- Account Status:\n- Notes:\n## Tracking & Analytics\n\n- Google Analytics 4 Property ID:\n- GA4 Access Level: (e.g. Editor / Viewer)\n- Google Search Console Access: Yes / No\n- UTM Naming Convention: (e.g. source / medium / campaign — describe format used)\n- Reporting Dashboard: (e.g. AgencyAnalytics / DashThis / Looker Studio — link if applicable)\n- Reporting Dashboard Link:\n## Internal Team — Who Manages This Account\n\n## Team Member Role Platforms They Date Assigned Date Removed\n\n## Manage\n\n## Account Log History\n\n## Accounts First Set Up / Accessed: (date)\n\n| Team Member | Role | Platforms They Manage | Date Assigned | Date Removed |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n\n## Flags & Important Notes\n\n- (Use this section for billing issues, account restrictions, spend escalations, policy violations, client-specific rules, or anything the team needs to know before touching this account)\n## Monthly Ad Account Verification Checklist\n\nRun this on the first Monday of every month for all active clients:\n\n## All ad accounts confirmed active and not restricted\n\n## Pixels and conversion tracking verified firing correctly\n\n## Monthly budget caps checked and still accurate\n\n## No unexpected charges or billing issues on any account\n\n## All team member access levels still correct\n\n## Spend pacing reviewed — on track for the month\n\n## Reporting dashboard updated and working\n\n## Last Account Review date updated above\n\n- Security Reminder: Never share ad account credentials, billing details, or payment methods via email, text, or\nClickUp comments. Always use the approved password manager. If you notice unauthorized changes to an ad account, notify your manager immediately and document it in the Notes & Flags section.\n\n## Example Completed Entry\n\n## Client Information\n\n- Client Name: Acme Wellness\n\n- \n- Billing Email: Same as above\n## Overall Ad Budget\n\n- Total Monthly Ad Spend Budget: $3,500\n- Budget Approved By: Jane Smith\n- Budget Approval Method: Signed SOW — January 2026\n- Spend Increase Approval Required? Yes\n- Spend Increase Threshold: Any increase over $500 requires written email approval from Jane Smith\n## Meta Ad Account\n\n- Business Manager Name: Acme Wellness BM\n- Business Manager ID: 1234567890\n- Ad Account Name: Acme Wellness — Main\n- Ad Account ID: 987654321\n- Access Type: Partner Access\n- Our Access Level: Admin\n- Pixel ID: 1122334455\n- Pixel Verified & Firing: Yes\n- Billing Method: Client's card on file\n- Monthly Spend Limit Set: Yes — $2,500\n- Facebook Page Linked: Yes — Acme Wellness\n- Instagram Account Linked: Yes — @acmewellness\n- Account Status: Active\n- Notes: Client runs occasional boosted posts independently — monitor for overlap with our campaigns\n\n- \n- Our Access Level: Admin\n- Conversion Tracking Set Up: Yes\n- Google Tag / GTM Active: Yes\n- Linked to GA4: Yes — GA4 Property ID: G-XXXXXXX\n- Linked to Google Search Console: Yes\n- Billing Method: Client's card on file\n- Monthly Budget Cap Set: Yes — $1,000\n- Account Status: Active\n- Notes: Search campaigns only — no display or YouTube approved yet\n## Internal Team\n\n## Team Member Role Platforms They Date Assigned Date Removed\n\n## Manage\n\n## Marcus T. Paid Media Lead Meta, Google Jan 15, 2026 —\n\n## Sarah R. Account Manager All (oversight) Jan 15, 2026 —\n\n## Account Log History\n\n- Accounts First Set Up / Accessed: Jan 15, 2026\n- First Campaign Launched: Jan 20, 2026\n- Last Account Review: June 1, 2026\n- Accounts Offboarded / Access Removed: —\n- Who Removed Access: —\n\n## Flags & Important Notes\n\n- Client requested we never pause campaigns on Fridays or weekends without her written approval — she\n\n| Team Member | Role | Platforms They Manage | Date Assigned | Date Removed |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| Marcus T. | Paid Media Lead | Meta, Google | Jan 15, 2026 | — |\n| Sarah R. | Account Manager | All (oversight) | Jan 15, 2026 | — |\n\n"
