    "date": "2026-07-09",
    "content": "## ✅ Onboarding Checklist\n\n### CRM & Communication\n- [ ] Deal marked Closed Won in CRM\n- [ ] Welcome email sent with intake form link within 24 hours (Template #8)\n- [ ] Intake form completed by client — confirmed in Google Forms Responses tab\n- [ ] Intake form follow-up sent if not submitted within 48 hours (Template #9)\n\n### Red Flag Review\n- [ ] Section 1 reviewed — approval timeline and decision makers checked\n- [ ] Section 3 reviewed — brand guide status checked\n- [ ] Section 4 reviewed — creative freedom level checked\n- [ ] Section 5 reviewed — services cross-referenced against signed SOW\n- [ ] Section 6 reviewed — goals and budget cross-referenced for expectation mismatch\n- [ ] Section 7 reviewed — agency history checked for red flags\n- [ ] Section 8 reviewed — platform access and admin status checked\n- [ ] Section 8B reviewed — access recovery noted if applicable\n- [ ] Section 9 reviewed — budget confirmed and cross-referenced with goals\n- [ ] Section 10 reviewed — start date cross-referenced with contract\n- [ ] All red flags logged in Deal record with section and question references\n- [ ] Red flags escalated to leadership and resolved before kick-off (if applicable)\n\n### Hub & Content Strategy\n- [ ] Logged into Hub with @revitalproductions.com email\n- [ ] Hub client profile created and populated with intake form data\n- [ ] Hub onboarding checklist started — all 3 phases\n- [ ] Content Strategy Builder completed using intake form data\n- [ ] Content Strategy Builder URL saved for reference\n- [ ] Strategy summary shared with delivery team\n\n### Sales → Delivery Handoff\n- [ ] Sales → Delivery Handoff form submitted (Growth → Onboarding Handoff → Sales → Delivery Handoff form)\n- [ ] Onboarding Handoff task description filled in (Platform Access, Red Flags, Links)\n- [ ] Onboarding Handoff task assigned to Delivery Lead\n- [ ] Delivery team notified and has reviewed the handoff task\n\n### ClickUp Workspace Setup\n- [ ] New client folder created from the ClickUp Template inside Delivery → Clients\n- [ ] Folder renamed with client company name\n- [ ] All 8 lists confirmed present inside the new folder\n- [ ] Status and custom fields confirmed to match Custom Field Options Reference doc\n- [ ] ClickUp tag created for this client (Settings → Tags → + Add Tag → client name)\n- [ ] Tag applied to all 7 tracker tasks in Master Shared Links Tracker once Zapier creates them\n\n### Shared View Links (6 total)\n- [ ] Campaign Briefs — shared view link generated, logged, verified in incognito\n- [ ] Content Calendar — shared view link generated, logged, verified in incognito\n- [ ] Active Projects & Tasks — shared view link generated, logged, verified in incognito\n- [ ] Completed Work — shared view link generated, logged, verified in incognito\n- [ ] Assets & Brand Files — shared view link generated, logged, verified in incognito\n- [ ] Reports & Analytics — shared view link generated, logged, verified in incognito\n- [ ] 🔗 All 6 shared view links logged in Master Shared Links Tracker\n\n### Form Links (2 total)\n- [ ] Campaign Briefs — Submit a Content Request form link generated and logged\n- [ ] Client Feedback & Revisions — Submit a Revision Request form link generated and logged\n- [ ] Both form links verified in incognito — test submission confirmed landing in correct client list\n- [ ] Both form links updated in client's portal doc buttons\n- [ ] 🔗 Both form links logged in Master Shared Links Tracker\n\n### Portal Setup\n- [ ] Client portal doc built from Client Welcome Template\n- [ ] All shared view links and form links pasted into portal doc\n- [ ] 🔐 Platform access logged in Access & Logins Tracker\n- [ ] 📣 Ad accounts logged in Client Ad Account Tracker\n- [ ] Access recovery platforms flagged if Section 8B was completed\n- [ ] Contact and Company records created in CRM with Role field set\n\n### Kick-Off Call\n- [ ] Kick-off call scheduled and confirmed (Template #10 sent)\n- [ ] Onboarding Handoff task shared with delivery team before call\n- [ ] Client Communication Policy (Part A) shared and explained during call\n- [ ] Portal walkthrough completed — client shown how to use Content Request and Revision Request forms\n- [ ] Red flag items addressed during kick-off call\n- [ ] Brand assets collected and uploaded\n- [ ] 📞 Call summary logged in Client Strategy Meeting Notes within 2 hours\n- [ ] Written follow-up email sent within 24 hours\n- [ ] Onboarding Handoff task status updated\n\n### Strategy & Production Setup\n- [ ] Initial audits run in Hub\n- [ ] Competitor analysis completed\n- [ ] First campaign brief submitted and approved\n- [ ] Content Calendar built based on Content Strategy Builder output\n- [ ] Client portal shared with client\n\n### Onboarding Complete\n- [ ] All Hub checklist items 100% complete\n- [ ] All platform access confirmed and logged\n- [ ] Onboarding Status updated to Active in CRM\n- [ ] 🟢 Client Health set to Green in CRM\n- [ ] Recurring deliverables and monthly check-ins set up in ClickUp\n- [ ] First monthly report or strategy review scheduled\n- [ ] Onboarding Handoff task status set to Complete\n\n*Last updated: July 2026 | Owner: Revital Productions Account Manager*\n"
